                        <interp inst="t18530613-name-28" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH BRAY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, H</hi> 49). I took the prisoner, who was pointed out to me by Nash—he said Nash was a false-swearing man, it was not him at all—I have known the prisoner for eight or nine years in that neighbourhood.</p>
